# Project Rules

This repo uses shared agent instructions and skills.

For any frontend, UI, layout, component, page, CSS, Tailwind, React, Next.js, Vite, or visual design task, read and apply:

- .agents/rules/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md

Core rules:
- Do not rewrite the app from scratch.
- Preserve existing routing.
- Preserve mock data unless explicitly requested.
- Do not call real APIs unless explicitly requested.
- Prefer small, safe refactors.
- Keep the UI clean, consistent, modern, and demo-ready.
- Run build/test after code changes when possible.
